    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been an absolute joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road! I\u2019ve loved every mile in this car, but it's time for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take her for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I do!",
      "price": 28900.0,
