      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2011 BMW M3 (E92) powered by the S65 4.0L V8, a masterpiece of engineering featuring an 8,400 RPM redline and eight individual throttle bodies. This unit is paired with a 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential, ensuring a raw, mechanical connection to the road. The vehicle is in good condition, with documented preventative maintenance on the rod bearings and updated throttle actuators\u2014essential for this high-revving platform. The EDC-equipped suspension provides adjustable damping for various road conditions, while the hydraulic steering offers superior tactile feedback. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the discerning purist, complete with service records to verify its mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
